exports[`citation > Gemini citation snapshot (issue #8880) > normalizeCitationMarks should insert [cite:N] at correct positions 1`] = `"**二氧化硫（$SO_2$）不能燃烧**，它是一种**不可燃**且通常**不助燃**的气体[cite:1][cite:2][cite:3]                                                                                     **不可燃性**：在日常和消防标准中，二氧化硫被明确归类为不燃气体[cite:1][cite:4][cite:5]   它本身就是硫或含硫化合物燃烧后的产物[cite:3][cite:6]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 **安全警告**：虽然二氧化硫本身不会燃烧，但需要注意的是，如果装有高压液态二氧化硫的钢瓶或储罐被卷入火灾中，受热会导致容器内压力急剧上升，有**发生物理爆炸**的危险[cite:1][cite:7]   此外，二氧化硫是一种具有强烈刺激性和腐蚀性的有毒气体，吸入会对人体呼吸道造成严重伤害[cite:1][cite:7][cite:5]     总结来说，二氧化硫自身绝对**不能燃烧**[cite:1][cite:7]"`;

exports[`citation > Gemini citation snapshot (issue #8880) > withCitationTags should produce correct final output 1`] = `"**二氧化硫（$SO_2$）不能燃烧**，它是一种**不可燃**且通常**不助燃**的气体[<sup data-citation='{&quot;id&quot;:1,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://example.com/teck&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;teck.com&quot;}'>1</sup>](https://example.com/teck)[<sup data-citation='{&quot;id&quot;:2,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://example.com/service-gov&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;service.gov.uk&quot;}'>2</sup>](https://example.com/service-gov)[<sup data-citation='{&quot;id&quot;:3,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://example.com/mozaweb&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;mozaweb.com&quot;}'>3</sup>](https://example.com/mozaweb)                                                                                     **不可燃性**：在日常和消防标准中，二氧化硫被明确归类为不燃气体[<sup data-citation='{&quot;id&quot;:1,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://example.com/teck&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;teck.com&quot;}'>1</sup>](https://example.com/teck)[<sup data-citation='{&quot;id&quot;:4,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://example.com/ivhhn&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;ivhhn.org&quot;}'>4</sup>](https://example.com/ivhhn)[<sup data-citation='{&quot;id&quot;:5,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://example.com/airliquide&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;airliquide.com&quot;}'>5</sup>](https://example.com/airliquide)   它本身就是硫或含硫化合物燃烧后的产物[<sup data-citation='{&quot;id&quot;:3,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://example.com/mozaweb&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;mozaweb.com&quot;}'>3</sup>](https://example.com/mozaweb)[<sup data-citation='{&quot;id&quot;:6,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://example.com/osha&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;osha.gov.tw&quot;}'>6</sup>](https://example.com/osha)                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 **安全警告**：虽然二氧化硫本身不会燃烧，但需要注意的是，如果装有高压液态二氧化硫的钢瓶或储罐被卷入火灾中，受热会导致容器内压力急剧上升，有**发生物理爆炸**的危险[<sup data-citation='{&quot;id&quot;:1,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://example.com/teck&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;teck.com&quot;}'>1</sup>](https://example.com/teck)[<sup data-citation='{&quot;id&quot;:7,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://example.com/ccohs&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;ccohs.ca&quot;}'>7</sup>](https://example.com/ccohs)   此外，二氧化硫是一种具有强烈刺激性和腐蚀性的有毒气体，吸入会对人体呼吸道造成严重伤害[<sup data-citation='{&quot;id&quot;:1,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://example.com/teck&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;teck.com&quot;}'>1</sup>](https://example.com/teck)[<sup data-citation='{&quot;id&quot;:7,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://example.com/ccohs&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;ccohs.ca&quot;}'>7</sup>](https://example.com/ccohs)[<sup data-citation='{&quot;id&quot;:5,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://example.com/airliquide&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;airliquide.com&quot;}'>5</sup>](https://example.com/airliquide)     总结来说，二氧化硫自身绝对**不能燃烧**[<sup data-citation='{&quot;id&quot;:1,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://example.com/teck&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;teck.com&quot;}'>1</sup>](https://example.com/teck)[<sup data-citation='{&quot;id&quot;:7,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://example.com/ccohs&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;ccohs.ca&quot;}'>7</sup>](https://example.com/ccohs)"`;
